      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a fantastic project car with tons of potential? This vehicle is the perfect choice for a DIY enthusiast or someone looking for a budget-friendly fixer-upper! While it needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to get back to its prime, it offers a solid starting point for your next restoration adventure. Grab this opportunity to give a car a second lease on life!",
